{"tid":4691,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"最屌釣魚法　俄男生殖器被魚含住上鉤","createTime":"2016-11-26T15:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T15:18:35.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb8e83daf8831411fc7dcc5083185db3860ccec","tid":4691,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/column/article/9/rnews/20160422/844419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F9%2Frnews%2F20160422%2F844419&d=wbblXAdUUDw7h6ZmuthJ0MW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=840f4dae\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/column/article/9/rnews/20160422/844419</a><br />\n（更新：新增41J配音版影片）<br />\n <br />\n俄羅斯一名男子日前到一處河邊挑戰裸泳，結果河中一條魚意外「上鉤」，把他的生殖器當成魚餌，咬住他的陰莖。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，這名裸男到河邊準備裸泳，攝影師兼好友的亞歷克斯(Alexei)還叮嚀他說：「注意！水裡有個洞，我曾經被類似魚類的東西咬過。」而裸男則回答：「我不怕！」之後裸男撲通一聲跳進河裡，不久之後，就聽見他的大叫聲，因為一條魚實實在在地把他的生殖器含住。<br />\n <br />\n裸男馬上上岸，試圖把魚從他的陰莖扯下來，但魚兒生命力強韌，拚命咬住裸男的「雞」，但之後裸男還是將這條魚扯下。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"8fcbf15dd6ae7d59a9d3fbaf9866b75510ded014","tid":4691,"uid":5944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:10:58.000Z","msg":"用普通話講上鉤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd964b160a15d7e17e4a6f243919a337ba12e48","tid":4691,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:13:12.000Z","msg":"施旖婕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7388c66c86fae6a1b568e856e011d0f3aeff78d","tid":4691,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用普通話講上鉤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上鳩"}]}